Package nz.ac.wgtn.swen225.lc.persistency

Record Class GameState

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
nz.ac.wgtn.swen225.lc.persistency.GameState
Record Components:
levelNumber - the current level being played.
mazeTiles - state of maze tile grid.
chap - the player chap object.
enemies - list of the enemy actors present.
chapInventory - keys present in Chap's inventory.
infoText - text shown by the level info tile.
public record GameState(int levelNumber, TileType[][] mazeTiles, Chap chap, List<EnemyActor> enemies, List<TileType> chapInventory, String infoText) extends Record
Record containing a Snapshot the State of Domain.
